{"title_page": "Sloup v \u010cech\u00e1ch", "text_new": "{{Infobox settlement\n| name                    = Sloup v \u010cech\u00e1ch\n| native_name             = \n| other_name              = \n| settlement_type         = Municipality and village\n<!-- images, nickname, motto -->\n| image_skyline           = Sloup (skaln\u00ed hrad) v \u010cech\u00e1ch (49).jpg\n| image_caption           = Village view\n| image_flag              = Flag of Sloup v Cechach.svg\n| image_shield            = Sloup v Cechach CoA CZ.svg\n| motto                   = \n| nickname                = \n| etymology               = \n<!-- location -->\n| subdivision_type        = Country\n| subdivision_name        = Czech Republic\n| subdivision_type1       = \n| subdivision_name1       = \n| subdivision_type2       = [[Regions of the Czech Republic|Region]]\n| subdivision_name2       = [[Liberec Region|Liberec]]\n| subdivision_type3       = [[Districts of the Czech Republic|District]]\n| subdivision_name3       = [[\u010cesk\u00e1 L\u00edpa District|\u010cesk\u00e1 L\u00edpa]]\n| subdivision_type4       = \n| subdivision_name4       = \n<!-- maps and coordinates -->\n| image_map               = \n| map_caption             = \n| pushpin_map             = Czech Republic\n| pushpin_relief          = 1\n| pushpin_map_caption     = Location in the Czech Republic\n| coordinates             = {{coord|50|44|20|N|14|35|20|E|display=inline,title}}\n| coordinates_footnotes   = \n<!-- government type, leaders -->\n| leader_title            = Mayor\n| leader_name             = Petra Makovick\u00e1\n<!-- established -->\n| established_title       = First mentioned\n| established_date        = 1318\n<!-- area -->\n| area_footnotes          = \n| area_total_km2          = 5.77\n| area_total_sq_mi        = \n| area_land_sq_mi         = \n| area_water_sq_mi        = \n<!-- elevation -->\n| elevation_footnotes     = \n| elevation_m             = 292\n<!-- population -->\n| population_as_of        = 2019-01-01<ref>{