itle=Gold Typhoon \u91d1\u724c\u5927\u98a8 |website=[[Gold Typhoon]] |language=Chinese |accessdate=29 May 2012 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120705041657/http://www.gold-typhoon.com.tw/music/album/5389 |archivedate=5 July 2012}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n{{Sigur R\u00f3s}}\n\n[[Category:2012 albums]]\n[[Category:Parlophone albums]]\n[[Category:Sigur R\u00f3s albums]]\n", "name_user": "Vanderelt", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eTrack listing", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Valtari"}
